	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hello,<br>I was wondering if anyone knew of a &quot;quicker&quot; way to switch between using instruments and weapons. It is nice to sit between battles with heal and mana song twisted and would like the bonus using the instrument gives me. However by the time I am able to get both weapons back in my hands the fight is almost over,in which case I look like I am not doing my part, or things are, or are close to getting out of control. Does anyone know of a quicker way to do this?<br>Thanks in advance for any help.<br><br>Keryn<br>Bard of 17 songs<br>E'CI server<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Sun Mar 24 19:59:36 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
