	   <a name=10170212962154></a>
	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f10170212962154><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=4&mid=10170212962154>RE: Instrument to weapon in less than 6.0 secs</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=4&mid=10170212962154#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=50234><span id=Sage>Hooray</span></a>, <span id=Sage>Sage</span><br><span id=notbold>65 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sun, Mar 24th 8:58 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.89]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>You can switch gear very quickly using hotbuttons. You can drag inventory slots to hotbuttons and drop/take stuff there.<br><br>My setup (not efficient, but i had no real time fiddling with it) looks as follows:<br><br>Forage		Primary Weapon Slot<br>Something	Instrument<br>Something	Secondary Weapon Slot<br>Instrument	Empty<br>Something	Instrument<br><br>If you switch to playing an instrument, single click primary, Instrument, seconday, empty (the 4 top buttons on right side, and viola, instrument.<br>It takes less than one second to switch that way.<br><br>To switch back, just click buttons in reverse order and you are back with weapons.<br><br>Palluin,<br>L31 Bard, severely underdressed.<br>&nbsp;<br>Nindor<br>L65 Dwarven Cleric on Zebuxoruk<br>Stone</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
