	   <tr><td colspan=2>Go buy some nice weapons, focus on low delay weapons to keep your Weapon skills maxed. Also, try to save up all your money for when you need it, good bards dont require much equipment at all to level. AT level 19, when you get invis, get a port to Cobalt Scar, go to Skyshrine, and sit there while *hopefully* people kill the Guardians/Sentries. ask if you can loot the corpses as most people will be there for Giant Faction. The Guardian has real nice stats and has a FABULOUS look to it with SoL graphics. You shouldnt need to re-equip until level 50 or so.<br><br>Good Luck<br><br>Torfin 42 Bard<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
